subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
lead_paragraph: Danica Patrick, who finished eighth in the Daytona 500, said she has no illusions that she will be a regular in the top 10. She planned to use the next races to establish her goals.
